299
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:11,520
Hurry! Move!

300
00:31:11,520 --> 00:31:12,440
- Mr. Shan! - Junhao!

301
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:14,170
- Junhao! - Junhao!

302
00:31:14,170 --> 00:31:15,310
How are they?

303
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:16,860
- Mr. Shan! - Junhao!

304
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:19,880
Yunyi!

305
00:31:20,710 --> 00:31:22,000
Be careful.

306
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:27,640
Junhao! Can you hear me, Junhao?

307
00:31:28,230 --> 00:31:29,280
Junhao!

308
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,430
Call an ambulance!

309
00:31:31,430 --> 00:31:33,230
Stay here. Don’t move. I’ll go check on Junhao.

310
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:35,430
Mr. Shan!

311
00:31:35,710 --> 00:31:36,470
Mr. Shan!

312
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,560
Mr. Shan!

313
00:31:42,540 --> 00:31:45,280
Junhao! Qianyu! Are you OK?

314
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:50,190
Junhao!

315
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:53,710
Junhao!

316
00:31:54,830 --> 00:31:56,000
- Mr. Shan! - Junhao!

317
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,590
Mr. Shan!

318
00:31:58,430 --> 00:31:59,430
Junhao!

319
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:02,010
- Wake up, Junhao! - Mr. Shan!

320
00:32:05,130 --> 00:32:07,520
Junhao, open your eyes, please!

321
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,600
Junhao!

322
00:32:15,710 --> 00:32:18,560
- Hello? We need an ambulance!
- Wake up!

323
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:20,160
Can you hear me, Junhao?

324
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:22,220
- Yes! Please wake up quickly!
- Junhao!

325
00:32:39,710 --> 00:32:41,880
He passed out. Is he gonna be OK?

326
00:32:43,790 --> 00:32:45,420
His head is bleeding.

327
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:52,310
Junhao! Junhao!

328
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:53,230
Slowly. Careful.

329
00:32:55,230 --> 00:32:57,190
Junhao! Junhao!

330
00:32:58,800 --> 00:32:59,470
Slowly.

331
00:32:59,470 --> 00:33:00,760
- Be careful. - Careful.

332
00:33:03,620 --> 00:33:07,940
= OR =

333
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:20,520
Excuse me,

334
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:22,040
did you see Miss Fan Yunyi?

335
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:22,800
No.

336
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:28,740
= Yunyi =

337
00:33:32,380 --> 00:33:35,530
- The number you’ve dialed can’t be reached.
- Pick up!

338
00:33:35,530 --> 00:33:37,120
Please try again later.

339
00:33:48,280 --> 00:33:50,230
Qianyu, let’s get you bandaged.

340
00:33:50,230 --> 00:33:51,560
I’m fine.

341
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:56,040
Why did you come?

342
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,000
It’s all your fault!

343
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:01,160
Mrs. Shan,

344
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:02,920
hadn’t it for her,

345
00:34:03,310 --> 00:34:05,310
your son’s condition would’ve become worse.

346
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:06,800
Yes, Chairman.

347
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:08,280
Qianyu injured herself

348
00:34:08,870 --> 00:34:10,190
in order to save Mr. Shan.

349
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:17,710
Qianyu, you should get treated, too.

350
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:28,150
Have a seat, Chairman.

351
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:38,080
Where did she go?

352
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:51,390
Hello?

353
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,040
Mrs. Lin,

354
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,390
is Yunyi at home?

355
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:55,520
No, she isn’t.

356
00:34:55,870 --> 00:34:57,000
Wait there.

357
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:58,360
If she gets back,

358
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,430
call me immediately.

359
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:00,910
Yes, Mr. Ziqian.

360
00:35:08,470 --> 00:35:10,560
Why is she walking in the street
in a wedding gown?

361
00:35:10,560 --> 00:35:11,670
Look.

362
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,000
What’s going on?

363
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:13,950
So odd.

364
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,120
Take some photos.

365
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:18,700
Gosh, is she crazy?

366
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:24,380
What happened to her?

367
00:35:24,380 --> 00:35:25,880
Why is she out like this?

368
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,600
Yeah. So weird.

369
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,760
- Let’s go. Let’s go. - Come on.

370
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:22,320
The patient was hit by heavy objects

371
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:24,470
and developed a subgaleal hematoma.

372
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:27,950
The severe blood loss caused his shock.

373
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:30,120
We’ve removed some clots

374
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:32,000
through puncture.

375
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:34,600
He should be OK.

376
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:37,520
Thank you very much, doctor.

377
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:38,570
You’re welcome.

378
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,320
Thank god Mr. Shan is fine.

379
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:43,800
Chairman,

380
00:36:44,190 --> 00:36:45,840
you still need to

381
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,320
handle the aftermath.

382
00:36:49,150 --> 00:36:50,000
Please.

383
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:59,430
Find out who did this.

384
00:36:59,430 --> 00:37:01,600
The culprit must pay for hurting Junhao!

385
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:03,280
Yes, Chairman.

386
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:04,430
The venue has been secured.

387
00:37:04,870 --> 00:37:06,080
I’ll investigate it now.

388
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:09,230
Ziqian?

389
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:11,150
What took you so long?

390
00:37:11,950 --> 00:37:13,080
Is Yunyi here?

391
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:15,600
No.

392
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:18,560
I didn’t see her

393
00:37:18,950 --> 00:37:19,950
after the accident.

394
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:22,760
No one took her here?

395
00:37:24,230 --> 00:37:25,390
It was a mess.

396
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,040
I also forgot.

397
00:37:27,040 --> 00:37:29,040
You only care about Junhao

398
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:31,670
but didn’t know Yunyi is missing?

399
00:37:32,520 --> 00:37:33,800
She can’t see anything!

400
00:37:34,230 --> 00:37:35,840
What if something happens to her?

401
00:37:38,190 --> 00:37:38,910
Zi...

402
00:37:40,710 --> 00:37:42,120
Yunyi is missing?

403
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:45,360
What are you waiting for, Dawei?

404
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:46,760
Go find her!

405
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:48,280
I’m on it.

406
00:38:13,210 --> 00:38:14,480
How are you holding up?

407
00:38:34,060 --> 00:38:37,340
Don’t take such risks ever again.

408
00:38:51,870 --> 00:38:52,830
I...

409
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:54,470
I’d save

410
00:38:55,190 --> 00:38:56,760
whoever was there.

411
00:39:03,040 --> 00:39:04,520
You regret it?

412
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:08,280
Regret what?

413
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,560
If not, why are you here?

414
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:20,280
I’m here to convince myself to give up.

415
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,120
Do you mean

416
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:25,040
you still haven’t?

417
00:39:32,950 --> 00:39:34,910
This is the third time I’ve saved you.

418
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:38,520
I must’ve owed you a ton

419
00:39:38,520 --> 00:39:40,230
in my previous lives.

420
00:39:40,950 --> 00:39:42,280
I owe you.

421
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:46,630
They can call me a cheating bastard

422
00:39:47,080 --> 00:39:48,190
or a selfish jerk.

423
00:39:48,870 --> 00:39:51,000
I don’t care.

424
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,470
I’ve decided

425
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,670
to cling on to you.

426
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:59,120
I’ll repay

427
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:02,840
what I owe you with the rest of my life.

428
00:40:21,470 --> 00:40:22,230
Mr. Ziqian.

429
00:40:22,230 --> 00:40:23,230
Is Yunyi back?

430
00:40:23,230 --> 00:40:24,360
No.

431
00:40:25,190 --> 00:40:26,430
Is everything OK?

432
00:40:26,430 --> 00:40:27,760
Where are Mrs. and Mr. Shan?

433
00:40:28,150 --> 00:40:29,150
Mr. Ziqian.

434
00:40:29,430 --> 00:40:30,520
What happened?

435
00:40:31,230 --> 00:40:32,320
Mr. Ziqian!

436
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,710
Qianyu,

437
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:24,280
Tonghao was in love with you

438
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:27,800
and so is Shan Junhao.

439
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:30,360
I guess

440
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,520
this is fate.

441
00:42:36,120 --> 00:42:37,190
It’s all your fault.

442
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:39,320
I was about to leave.

443
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:42,120
I didn’t realize

444
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:43,950
until the accident happened

445
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:46,430
that I cannot stop caring about you.

446
00:42:48,430 --> 00:42:50,000
I won’t allow you to run away from me.

447
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:55,520
That’s irresponsible.

448
00:42:56,230 --> 00:42:57,760
You’re already married.

449
00:42:59,390 --> 00:43:01,000
I didn’t make the vow.

450
00:43:01,630 --> 00:43:03,360
Don’t go against your heart.

451
00:43:13,390 --> 00:43:14,080
Come here.

452
00:43:14,520 --> 00:43:15,190
What?

453
00:43:16,150 --> 00:43:18,360
I want to take a closer look at you.

454
00:43:19,280 --> 00:43:20,560
What’s there to look?

455
00:43:29,870 --> 00:43:31,600
What’s wrong? It hurts again?

456
00:43:37,230 --> 00:43:38,320
Got you!

457
00:43:42,560 --> 00:43:45,150
Your eyes have given you away.

458
00:43:47,080 --> 00:43:48,560
What?

459
00:43:49,630 --> 00:43:51,000
From now on,

460
00:43:51,520 --> 00:43:53,040
you cannot leave me again.

461
00:43:54,040 --> 00:43:54,760
Let go.

462
00:43:55,230 --> 00:43:55,950
No.

463
00:43:55,950 --> 00:43:56,840
Let go of me!

464
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:57,560
I won’t.

465
00:43:57,980 --> 00:43:59,500
- Let go! - No!

466
00:44:00,630 --> 00:44:02,040
What are you doing here?

467
00:44:02,600 --> 00:44:03,670
Mrs. Shan.

468
00:44:05,320 --> 00:44:05,820
Mom.

469
00:44:05,820 --> 00:44:07,000
I’m leaving.

470
00:44:08,280 --> 00:44:08,910
Qianyu.

471
00:44:08,910 --> 00:44:09,840
Junhao.

472
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,600
Yunyi is missing!

473
00:44:14,840 --> 00:44:15,760
What?

474
00:44:20,600 --> 00:44:21,470
Get out!

