00:45:31,280 --> 00:45:36,300
♪ Distance between us ♪

476
00:45:39,600 --> 00:45:44,690
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

477
00:45:45,750 --> 00:45:49,730
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

478
00:45:49,750 --> 00:45:53,440
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

479
00:45:53,990 --> 00:46:01,390
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

480
00:46:02,630 --> 00:46:06,930
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

481
00:46:06,950 --> 00:46:10,710
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

482
00:46:10,950 --> 00:46:15,190
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

483
00:46:15,210 --> 00:46:18,720
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

484
00:46:19,230 --> 00:46:23,390
♪ You painted my life ♪

485
00:46:23,410 --> 00:46:26,990
♪ With flowers ♪

486
00:46:27,010 --> 00:46:30,950
♪ You raised me up ♪

487
00:46:30,970 --> 00:46:34,370
♪ From that moment on ♪

488
00:46:34,900 --> 00:46:37,660
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪
